text: SSV Reutlingen 05 is a German football club based in Reutlingen, Baden- Württemberg. == History == The club was founded as FC Arminia Reutlingen and was renamed SV Reutlingen 1905 in 1910. == Other websites == * Official website Category:1905 establishments in Germany Category:Football clubs in Baden-Württemberg
